				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: MPG Trials<a name="66811"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Oct 13 04 11:15 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>I went on my first one the other night.  We fought to the Power (?) trial (nice exp !!) and then clicked in on a totem pole thing (one group).  We did the destruction one where you have to kill a certain amount of mobs in a certain amount of time (12 mins?).  The mobs pop and aggro you but the most we had at once was 2... possibly 3.  They are dark blue to me (lvl 67) and didn't hit that hard. Noboby died but we were timed out on the last mob <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-9.gif" border="0" alt="Crying" hspace="2" />  The mob just poofed and we medded up and gated out.  
<br />

<br />
You get yellow warning messages about 5 minutes left, 4 minutes left etc.  We could have done it except once or twice the mob got pushed up the wall so our DPS was lowered when we couldn't reach it that well.
<br />

<br />
I can't wait to do another - it was great fun.  And I scored the Maze Runner's Mask from clearning mobs on the way to the trial. <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-11.gif" border="0" alt="Cool" hspace="2" /></span></td>
