				<td colspan="2"><span>We had no problems on the power boss with a 10k unbuffed tank. Pure melee fight, don't think there were any shenanigans like him getting stronger. You just need the DPS to kill all the mobs within the time limit. We had 1 minute spare with a War/SK/BST/Bard/Shaman/Cleric group. The trash mobs don't hit hard so we were just tanking them all, doing a PoV/Zek/Trusik/Marr twist (yeah I have gimp songs).
<br />

<br />
The challenge is having enough DPS to get to the boss fight.
<br />

