Each projection gives you a choice  like the Projection of Mind gives you the Fear trial or Hatred trial..YOU choose which you want.
<br />

<br />
If you fail a trial, you're locked out from it and ALL other trials for 2 hours I believe...somewhere in that vicinity.
<br />

<br />
