				<td colspan="2"><span>A group of 62+ would not be able to handle MPG even if they could zone in.  The trials are designed for levels 70s ep/time+ geared, a 10k+ unbuffed tank is highly recommended for each trial as healing will be close every single time.
<br />

<br />
Ingenuity will be close no matter how you do it.  Named is immune to all forms of damage accept through bane and whatever he does to himself.  Once tank on named take a few minutes to get at least 1 bane weapon on a few people, the clicky on bane weaps is 800dd 6 sec cast.  Tank will need to be chain CHd from cleric.
<br />

<br />
Power, just think raw dps.  Use best ae slow/dot song and get the mobs tight.  The dmg output from these mobs is mediocre at best.
<br />

<br />
Trials are great fun and amazing loot for the risk, the 3 day lockout on win makes me sad though.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
